files.name: .gitignore
files.content:
# Compiled source #
###################
*.com
*.class
*.dll
*.exe
*.o
*.so

# Packages #
############
# it's better to unpack these files and commit the raw source
# git has its own built in compression methods
*.7z
*.dmg
*.gz
*.iso
*.jar
*.rar
*.tar
*.zip

# Logs and databases #
######################
*.log
*.sql
*.sqlite

# OS generated files #
######################
.DS_Store*
thumbs.db
.idea
.vagrant
Icon?
Thumbs.db
*.sublime-workspace
*.sublime-project
*.sass-cache
.sass-cache
/.sass-cache
/build
npm-debug.log
node_modules
/workshop
/testvagrant
/workshop.zip
package.box
